data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a charming and established neighborhood! This delightful property offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. With three spacious bedrooms and a meticulously designed one bathroom featuring a double vanity, this home is ideal. Boasting 1750 square feet of finished living space, this residence offers an abundance of room for your needs. The one-car garage, complete with additional storage, ensures that you have ample space for your vehicles and all of your belongings. Step inside and be greeted by a bonus den on the lower level, complete with a cozy gas log fireplace. This inviting space is perfect for relaxation and unwinding after a long day. The downstairs area also features updated cabinetry that can be transformed into a workspace or a second kitchen, giving you plenty of options for customization. For those who love outdoor living, the double-tier back deck is a true gem. It overlooks a spacious backyard with a partially fenced area, providing a safe and private space for outdoor activities. Gardening enthusiasts will appreciate the two large sheds, one of which comes equipped with electricity, making it a perfect workshop or storage space.Situated in a desirable location, this home is conveniently close to shopping and medical facilities, making daily errands a breeze. The main level laundry adds convenience to your daily routine, while updated flooring throughout the house ensures a modern and polished look.Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a visit today to experience the comfort, convenience, and charm of this move in ready property.
